_sText:
This map was designed to be fast and quick, but with enough cover to not be totally visible to others.  The upper portion was added as a risk/reward device, the idea was if you are up there you have a total vision field for the most part, but this makes you visible to everyone else and the floors are designed so they can be shot through.
